             was indicted for <rs id="t18101031-5-off21" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18101031-5-off21" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18101031-5-off21" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18101031-5-cd22" type="crimeDate">6th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18101031-5-off21 t18101031-5-cd22"></join>, a wrapper, value 1 s, and two hundred yards of calico, value 20 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18101031-5-victim109" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Russell
                  <interp inst="t18101031-5-victim109" type="surname" value="Russell"></interp>
